  "2026-06-26T18:50:54.481Z",codex-codefactor-sdk-cli-20260626,"Investigation note: live 2026-06-26 CodeFactor public issues page reports A rating, 601 analyzed files, 172 issues after the merged maintainability branch; PM snapshot still tracks remaining complexity and duplication children. GitHub state: no open PRs, no open Dependabot or code-scanning alerts; issue #374 remains open and externally blocked on missing RELEASE_PAT in release environment; pnpm audit --audit-level moderate reports no known vulnerabilities. Dependency drift from pnpm outdated: @sentry/cli 3.5.1 -> 3.6.0, @sentry/node 10.61.0 -> 10.62.0, @types/node held at Node 22 types despite latest 26.x."
  "2026-06-26T19:05:47.605Z",codex-codefactor-sdk-cli-20260626,"Evidence update: CodeFactor remediation bundle now covers the remaining duplication primitives and generated/test analysis scope. Verification passed: pnpm build; targeted 254-test suite; pnpm contracts:check; pnpm quality:static; pnpm typecheck; pnpm security:scan; full coverage 100/100/100/100 across 5133 tests; manual isolated temp-project smoke with PM_PATH/PM_GLOBAL_PATH passed package install/doctor and shared unset behavior. Remaining release issue #374 is external to code changes: GitHub scheduled Auto Release requires RELEASE_PAT in the release environment."
  "2026-06-26T19:06:27.162Z",codex-codefactor-sdk-cli-20260626,"Changelog evidence: pnpm changelog:pm:check installed pm-changelog 2026.6.20, activated changelog export/generate commands, and reported CHANGELOG.md unchanged with item_count=1353 and bytes=217874."
  "2026-06-26T19:07:02.161Z",codex-codefactor-sdk-cli-20260626,"Observability evidence: sentry issue list returned recent unresolved CLI issue records with scrubbed paths and useful short IDs/permalinks; sentry-telemetry-gate passed for unbrained/pm-cli with critical=0, high=0, access_ok=true, token_source=SENTRY_PERSONAL_ADMIN_TOKEN, and telemetry finish_error_rate_pct=0.66 with failures_without_error_code_rows=0. pm telemetry stats showed 13 queued rows, 0 invalid rows, recent health/stats finish events, and 0 local error_rate for sampled finish rows."
  "2026-06-26T19:15:44.087Z",codex-codefactor-sdk-cli-20260626,"Review response: addressed Sourcery/Gemini feedback on PR #380 by replacing UPDATE_UNSET_FIELD_DEFINITIONS slice-based insertion with named shared groups around close-reason and documenting why core mutation option keys must stay aligned with CLI unset metadata without importing CLI modules into core. Verification after review fix passed pnpm build, pnpm quality:static, pnpm contracts:check, and targeted create/update/SDK tests (3 files, 313 tests)."
